mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00000A;
mso-font-kerning:1.5pt;mso-ansi-language:PT-BR;mso-fareast-language:EN-US">§ 4°</span></i></b><i style="mso-bidi-font-style:normal"><span style="font-size:11.0pt;line-height:
115%;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;
mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00000A;mso-font-kerning:1.5pt;mso-ansi-language:
PT-BR;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold"> O Poder Executivo
divulgará permanentemente em seu site oficial o andamento das metas e dos
indicadores de desempenho estabelecidos no Plano de Metas, mantendo-os
atualizados em tempo real. </span></i><span style="font-size:11.0pt;line-height:
115%;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;
mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00000A;mso-font-kerning:1.5pt;mso-ansi-language:
PT-BR;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold"><a href="https://camarasempapel.cmv.es.gov.br/Arquivo/Documents/legislacao/html/E692018.html#a1"><span style="mso-ansi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%">(Redação dada pela Emenda à
Lei Orgânica nº 69/2018)</span></a><i style="mso-bidi-font-style:normal"><span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></i></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-indent:70.9pt;line-height:
115%;mso-hyphenate:none;text-autospace:ideograph-other"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style:
normal"><span style="font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00000A;
mso-font-kerning:1.5pt;mso-ansi-language:PT-BR;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;
mso-bidi-font-weight:bold"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></i></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-indent:70.9pt;line-height:
115%;mso-hyphenate:none;text-autospace:ideograph-other"><b><i style="mso-bidi-font-style:
normal"><span style="font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;
